      • navigate

        public void navigate​(javafx.event.ActionEvent event,
                     java.lang.String fxmlLocation,
                     java.lang.String title)
              throws java.io.IOException
        Navigate to requested menu. Upon activating event handler via button, handles navigation to menu.
        Parameters:
        event - ActionEvent instantiated via event handler tied to button.
        fxmlLocation - String of fxml file location of desired menu.
        title - String of title.
        Throws:
        java.io.IOException - if stage or scene can't be set.
